Title: Evolution (1)
Plot: The team investigates an unstoppable new enemy soldier engineered by Anubis. Dr. Jackson leads a team in search of an alien device in Central America, but gets more than he bargained for.
Director: Peter DeLuise, Damian Kindler, Michael Shanks
GuestStars: Frank Roman, Zak Santiago Alam, Sean Whale, Todd Thomson, Eric Breker, Michael Jonsson, Dan Payne, Victor Favrin, Craig Erickson
